User

Description: Base user data that discord provides

Fields

Name Type Attributes Required Comment
id String
  • @id
 Yes Users ID (snowflake)
username String
  • -
Yes User name, not unique
discriminator String
  • -
Yes Users four digit discord tag
avatar String?
  • -
No Users avatar
bot Boolean?
  • -
No Is the user a bot?
system Boolean?
  • -
No Is the user a Discord System user?
mfa_enabled Boolean?
  • -
No MFA Enabled?
banner String?
  • -
No Banner
accent_color Int?
  • -
No Accent Color
locale String?
  • -
No Locale
verified Boolean?
  • -
No Verified?
email String?
  • -
No Email
flags Int?
